'''嗅觉丧失'''是指失去对一种或多种[[气味|气味]]的检测能力，即嗅觉、味觉的喪失<ref name="Coon2006">{{Cite book|last=Coon|first=Dennis|last2=Mitterer|first2=John|format=vanc|title=Introduction to Psychology: Gateways to Mind and Behavior|date=2006|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-0-495-09155-4|page=174|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=V6EHmNCmEWQC&pg=PA174|language=en}}</ref><ref name="Jon2010">{{Cite book|last=Jones|first=Nicholas|title=Practical Rhinology|date=2010|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=978-1-4441-0861-3|page=25|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=arSSpm-OgjYC&pg=PA25|language=en|access-date=2020-10-10|archive-date=2021-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210828150805/https://books.google.com/books?id=arSSpm-OgjYC&pg=PA25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。嗅觉丧失可能是暂时或永久性的。

嗅觉丧失可能是由于多种因素引起的，包括鼻粘膜[[炎症|发炎]]、[[鼻腔|鼻腔通道]]阻塞或一个[[颞叶|颞叶]]遭破坏。炎症是由于[[鼻竇|鼻旁窦]]内壁和中、上鼻甲的慢性粘膜變化所致。

